data.description: Location! Location! CBS Home with detached Garage!  South Middle River neighborhood!  This 3 bedroom, 1 bath home, includes a large extra room for a third bedroom  Newly renovated kitchen and bath, with fresh paint throughout, inside laundry room and a 2022 tankless water heater. The outside has been completely re-stuccoed and painted.  A brand new metal roof on both the home and garage finishes the polished look!  Large and private fenced in backyard with sprinkler system.  Garage already has electric and water hook ups. Minutes from Flagler Village and Wilton Manors.  Motivated Seller!
